    - [Config] USB_G_MULTI=m

  * Miscellaneous upstream changes
    - configs: Enable the AD193x codecs
    - overlays: balenaFin v1.1.0 carrier board update
    - configs: Add CONFIG_LEDS_PCA963X=m

