  [ Ubuntu: 4.13.0-13.14 ]

  * linux: 4.13.0-13.14 -proposed tracker (LP: #1720239)
  * [Bug] USB 3.1 Gen2 works as 5Gbps (LP: #1720045)
    - xhci: set missing SuperSpeedPlus Link Protocol bit in roothub descriptor
